{"tid":2192262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何俊堯調職七月前已決定 與投訴無關 杜浩成及張天雁曾擔任相同職位","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T05:13:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7202723b11ed5d1e87c5a1c14df7a5f094eddf2d","tid":2192262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"東區裁判法院裁判官何俊堯早前受到「藍絲」群起去信投訴，指他早前審理區議員仇栩欣涉襲警案時立場偏頗，對警方懷有強烈敵意。及後立法會議員葛珮帆再去信終審法院首席法官馬道立，要求嚴肅跟進，更指何俊堯過去審理多宗涉及反修例示威案時裁決不公，「放生」被告。根據司法機構網頁顯示，何官將調任高等法院刑事案件排期法官，惟據知調職的決定並非突然，實早於今年七月之前已定，與投訴無關，而過往亦有多位裁判官曾任該職位。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，過往裁判官杜浩成及張天雁曾擔任此職位，兩人現分別於觀塘及九龍城裁判法院審案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/YG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FYG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=5d9133dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FYG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU%2F&h=351ae3fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/YG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU/</a>"},{"pid":"62a24ee243ed11ae809575bfbd6c749e8567459f","tid":2192262,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12f8fc0def5f6149c2a3162c0b5da5993f7a37f","tid":2192262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62a24ee243ed11ae809575bfbd6c749e8567459f","tid":2192262,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />